##Haidilao response customer confirmed new pneumonia: The shop has been fully disinfected, the staff is currently in normal physical condition

In recent days, Changzhou, Jiangsu Province, issued a notice on emergency spread and search for relevant contacts: When screening confirmed cases of COVID-19 infection in Changzhou, the 27th confirmed case (male) was found to have dined with friends at Haidilao hotpot restaurant (Fengchen International, Xinbei District) at Table No. 93 at 18:47(Male 4, female 1) at 18:47:43 on January 22, two have been diagnosed with COVID-19 pneumonia and three have been put under medical observation.

In response, a relevant person in charge of Haidilao told interface news that the Fengchen international store in Xinbei District, Changzhou, was part of the customer's numerous behavioral trajectories. After receiving notification from relevant departments, the store actively cooperated with the quarantine inspection, the store is actively cooperating with the epidemic prevention agency in collecting and feedback customer information, liaising with the contact designated by the authorities, and paying close attention to the staff who have served customers and are currently in normal physical condition.

According to the epidemic prevention work briefing in Haidilao, the company set up a prevention and control team on January 23 to set up a third-party Expert Advisory Team to optimize prevention and control.

According to Interface News, the General Command of Haidilao Group's epidemic prevention is under the command of Chairman Jang Yong, from the Organization structure, store staff placement and epidemic prevention, emergency reporting mechanism, material supply distribution, fund management and other aspects of division of responsibility.

On January 23, Haidilao set up Wuhan Store Epidemic Prevention Field Headquarters, Wuhan Store Manager as the General Command of the scene, responsible for 27 stores in Wuhan Area Epidemic Response and staff placement. In addition, Haidilao headquarters set up 16 psychological counseling team, psychological counseling for employees.

Today, the General Command of Haidilao epidemic prevention donated 40,000 boxes of self-cooking hotpot to Wuhan Jinyintan Hospital and Wuhan University People's Hospital. From February 12, Haidilao will donate 20,000 boxes of self-cooking hotpot to health care workers in Hubei every day through the Hubei Provincial Charity General Association until the situation in Hubei stabilizes.

Earlier, Interface News reported that on February 2, Haidilao issued a notice that, in view of the recent development of the epidemic, the closure of mainland stores will continue to extend. The company had decided to suspend operations in its mainland stores from January 26 to 31. The company's delivery service has also been suspended.
